      "description": "\n<figure class=\"tmblr-full\" data-orig-height=\"3000\" data-orig-width=\"3000\"><img src=\"https://64.media.tumblr.com/1cef239a2e7573c61a12cd87b72f30e3/e29594c7653b8c4d-7a/s540x810/6f044f8144543f7b21d0937de92b8e65996997cb.jpg\" data-orig-height=\"3000\" data-orig-width=\"3000\"></figure><p>Our latest release is an EP from BONE CUTTER, a new band formed from the ashes of Heavy Heavy Low Low and includes producer Sam Pura. This EP is 4 tracks of in-your-face punk with a lot of weird twists.</p>\n<p>Listen to the first track of their upcoming EP on BrooklynVegan now @ <a href=\"https://www.brooklynvegan.com/heavy-heavy-low-low-members-form-bone-cutter-watch-the-video-for-their-debut-song/?fbclid=IwAR01PA5zocXbEaUH2rIHWspsP4UtkLBjv_7v3ztBBM_K_9JN0xHdLlau4IE\">https://www.brooklynvegan.com/heavy-heavy-low-low…/</a><br></p>\n<p>This will have a physical release as well, but details and more information are to be announced. Stay tuned!</p>\n",
